title: Sword Master VR
description: Sword Master VR brings you intense sword fighting gameplay that has never been possible in traditional video games. Taking full advantage of the HTC Vive's room-scale virtual reality, you must learn to fight with realistic swords in full 360 combat! React quickly, duck and dodge, deflect incoming attacks! Sword Master VR is not a game of standing still and lightly wiggling your sword in the enemies face. Sword Master VR is a game of endurance, skill, speed, and most importantly, to become a master of the blade
